  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Inquiry report on Nimal to President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The inquiry report on former Minister Nimal Siripala de Silva has been handed over to the President's Secretary.",
        "A report has been handed over to the President's Secretary at the President's Secretariat this afternoon (31).",
        "There were reports on various social networking sites that a cabinet minister had demanded a bribe from a Japanese company.",
        "Former minister Nimal Siripala de Silva had demanded an inquiry into the matter.",
        "It is noteworthy that President Ranil Wickremesinghe had appointed a three-member investigation team on the 22nd of last year as per the request made by Nimal Siripala de Silva. (a)"
      ],
